Package com.illposed.osc.utility

Provides utility classes, used internally by the Java OSC API classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JavaRegexAddressSelector
    Checks whether an OSC Address Pattern matches a given Java regular expression.
    OSCByteArrayToJavaConverter
    Utility class to convert a byte array, conforming to the OSC byte stream format, into Java objects.
    OSCJavaToByteArrayConverter
    OSCJavaToByteArrayConverter is a helper class that translates from Java types to their byte stream representations according to the OSC spec.
    OSCPacketDispatcher
    Dispatches OSCPackets to registered listeners (Methods).
    OSCPatternAddressSelector
    Checks whether an OSC message address matches a given wildcard expression, as specified in the OSC protocol specification.

Package com.illposed.osc.utility Description

Provides utility classes, used internally by the Java OSC API classes. Users of the library should not need to use these classes directly.
